A. The Color Backgrounds:

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <title>HTML Backgrounds Application</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h3>HTML Backgrounds Application</h3>
        <table bgcolor="#808080" width="100%">
            <tr>
                <td>
                    This is background A<br />
                    This color is grey<br />
                    Here we shall talk about HTML
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <table bgcolor="#ff00ff" width="100%">
            <tr>
                <td>
                    This is background B<br />
                    This color is pink<br />
                    Here we shall talk about CSS
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </body>
</html>

